              }
            }
          },
          "_name": "header12",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"header12\" group=\"Headers\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Wrap Bg\" name=\"wrapBgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-1920x1369.jpg\" selected>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ff6666\">\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"card col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-9\">\n                <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"card-box align-center\">\n                        <h1 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><b>Advertising predictions in 2023</b></h1>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">Click any text to edit or style it. Select\n                            text to insert a link. Click blue \"Gear\" icon in the top right corner to hide/show buttons,\n                            text, title and change the block background. Click red \"+\" in the bottom right corner to add\n                            a new block. Use the top left menu to create new pages, sites and add themes.</p>\n                        <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\">\n                            <a class=\"btn btn-secondary-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Start Now &gt;</a>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "tlgqdRmx8H",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {},
          "_anchor": "header12-35"
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "background-color": "@bgColor"
          },
          "_name": "content5",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"content5\" group=\"Content\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"10\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\">\n                    <b>Article Title</b>\n                </h3>\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\"></h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">It's no secret that advertising is evolving. And, as we move into a new decade, it's only going to continue to change and grow. So, what will the most popular advertising platforms be in 2023? Here are a few predictions:<br><br><b>1. Social media will still be a major player.</b><br>Social media platforms like Facebook, Instagram, and Snapchat will continue to be popular among advertisers. Why? Because they offer a huge audience reach and allow you to target specific demographics.<br><br><b>2. Video advertising will become even more popular.</b><br>Video is already a powerful marketing tool, and it's only going to become more popular in the next few years. As platforms like YouTube and Instagram launch new video features, advertisers will flock to them to reach their target audiences.<br><br><b>3. Native advertising will grow in popularity.</b><br>Native advertising is a type of advertising that blends in with the content on a website or app. It's less intrusive than traditional banner ads, and users are more likely to engage with it. As ad blocking continues to rise, native advertising will become an increasingly attractive option for advertisers.<br><br><b>4. Programmatic advertising will become the norm.</b><br>Programmatic advertising is a form of online advertising that uses algorithms to target ads at specific audiences. It's efficient and effective, and it's quickly becoming the preferred method for many advertisers. Programmatic ad spending is expected to grow from $32 billion in 2017 to $45 billion by 2019.<br><br><b>5. Voice search ads will start to take off.</b><br>Voice search is starting to take off as more and more people use voice-activated assistants like Siri, Alexa, and Google Assistant. And as more people use voice search, businesses are starting to take notice and produce ads specifically for voice search. Voice search ads are still in their infancy, but they offer several advantages over traditional text-based ads. For one, they can be more targeted since they can be based on the specific keywords that were used in the voice search. And since voice searches are usually done on mobile devices, these ads can be targeted to users based on their location. One disadvantage of voice search ads is that they can be harder to create than traditional text-based ads. But as voice search becomes more popular, we expect that businesses will start to invest more in creating these types of ads.<br><br>-<br><br>The most popular advertising trends will likely include traditional and modern techniques. Traditional advertising techniques such as print ads, television commercials, and radio ads will still be used. Still, they will be supplemented with modern techniques such as online advertising, social media marketing, and content marketing. As consumers become more media-savvy, they will increasingly ignore traditional advertising techniques that are not relevant to their interests or needs. This means that advertisers will need to be more creative and strategic in their approach to reach their target audiences. Some of the most popular advertising trends next year should include the following.<br><br><b> 1. Online Advertising: </b>Online advertising will continue to grow in popularity due to its effectiveness and reach. Advertisers can target specific demographics with online ads and track the results of their campaigns easily. <br><br><b>2. Social Media Marketing:</b> Social media platforms such as Facebook, Twitter, and Instagram will be used increasingly by advertisers to reach their target audiences. Advertisers can build relationships with potential customers and create brand loyalty by creating engaging content. <br><br><b>3. Content Marketing:</b> Content marketing is a form of marketing that focuses on creating and distributing valuable content to attract and retain customers. Advertisers can use content marketing to build relationships with their target audiences and create brand awareness. <br><br><b>4. Mobile Advertising:</b> Mobile devices such as smartphones and tablets are being used more frequently to access the internet, making mobile advertising an essential part of any marketing campaign. Advertisers can reach their target audiences through mobile ads, SMS campaigns, and apps. <br><br><b>5. Data-Driven Advertising:</b> Data-driven advertising is a form of marketing that uses data analysis to improve the effectiveness of campaigns. Advertisers can use data from customer surveys, website analytics, and social media platforms to segment their target audiences and tailor their messages accordingly.<br><br><br>November 1st, 2022<br></p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
